column5: One of my good fishing buds came for a visit last night and we had some cold ones while chatting about fishing. Well, a few hours later and about 7-8 tall boys, we called it a night.  Woke up this morning realizing that I can't indulge like I used too, lol. I still like to have beers, just not that many.  So in short, here is what booze made me do    Walleye, eggs, panfries, bacon, english muffin and some ice tea
all that's missing is a breakfast caesar.
Nice breakfast!!!  Hope there's no "after" shot of it!!!
wow if you're going to whip up a breakfast like that you can drink at my place anytime
Breakfast of Champions Al thats missing is a bit of the Hair of the Dog Shake remover.
Are you not allowed near the good china when hung over?
I was thinking the same thing!!  The food looks ok...it's the hub cap I was wondering about.
hahahaha, it was too much to fit on our plates, and I was craving this so bad I would have ate it off the floor
just drink more beer and you should be ok
Looks good. But give me a big tin of Hienz tomato juice and a six pack and i'm good.
im hungry now, havent had fish in a long long time
yeah thats nice, but where's the beer? lol  man this reminds me of my college days!  we used to have bacon grease toast and busch lite every thursday/friday morning.  glad those days are over!
ahah that happens far too frequently around here
